      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Not only are you able to attack and skate on the ice, but you can combine
    the two!!



    A trail will follow behind you when using the demonstrated input,
    if the trail is looped back on then the ice will be cut!



    leaving behind
    a gaping chasm to cold water!

    These are as dangerous to you as they are
    to goblins'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
