  m_text: "Alone on the rink during your nightly training, you are suddenly faced
    with hoards of goblins... \n\nThe aim of the game is to score the most points
    by surviving as many waves of goblins as possible,  building up your attack combo
    and relinquishing the goblins of their lives!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
